    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c204-103">由于基于任务的异步编程模型倾向于抽象地使用线程，因此 <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> 实例可用于跨线程保存数据。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c204-103">Because the task-based asynchronous programming model tends to abstract the use of threads, <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> instances can be used to persist data across threads.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7c204-104">当与当前线程关联的值发生更改时，<xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> 类还提供可选通知，这是因为它是通过设置 <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601.Value%2A> 属性显式更改的，或在线程遇到 `await` 或其他上下文转换时隐式更改。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7c204-104">The <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601> class also provides optional notifications when the value associated with the current thread changes, either because it was explicitly changed by setting the <xref:System.Threading.AsyncLocal%601.Value%2A> property, or implicitly changed when the thread encountered an `await` or other context transition.</span></span>  
  
   
  
